events.description: A 2018 incident in rural New Mexico, USA, remains shrouded in mystery. A witness reported seeing a strange object descending from the sky and crashing into a field. According to the account, the craft was estimated to be around 30 feet long and had a distinctive shape. The pilot's body was recovered, but their whereabouts remain unknown. Despite numerous investigations and eyewitness accounts, the cause of the crash and its contents are still unexplained.
